latestPosts.caption:
Piya Bawari – a classic from the movie Khoobsurat, performed by the iconic Rekha. Here’s my little attempt at recreating this beautiful choreography on a kavit, with Asha Bhosle’s magical voice.

Can’t believe three years ago I never thought I’d be able to dance like this! Huge thanks to my Guruji @rajendrachaturvedi for always pushing me and believing in me—it’s a long journey, but his guidance keeps me going.

Big love to @minal_gaur and @seema___purohit ♥️♥️✨

Also, dancing in a sari? A whole skill of its own!
